QuestData.Title: Free From Her Clutches
QuestData.Description: The Shek'zeer manipulators are corralling young kunchong into that clutch and exposing them to raw fear energies, twisting them and accelerating their growth.$B$BDisgusting! I will not allow it!$B$BBreak open the cages and set those hatchlings free.
QuestData.LogDescription: Break open Kunchong Cages to release 8 Kunchong Hatchlings in the Clutches of Shek'zeer.
